ns0:Concept.displayName: Naloxone 0.5 MG / Pentazocine 50 MG Oral Tablet

ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of RxNorm codes is intended to capture orders of any medication containing pentazocine (other than formulations containing naloxone).),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who are prescribed pentazocine (other than formulations containing naloxone).),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNorm codes associated with pentazocine are included in the value set.),(Exclusion Criteria: Medications without pentazocine are excluded from the value set.)
